// Product role: pro companion surface. Hidden BUS bindings remain operator-only; the visible surface mode controls the user-facing dashboard cut.
// Product scope: this dashboard reflects the long-dip specialist mainline of SMC Core.
//   Short-parity would require a dedicated companion track; it is not an implicit promise of this surface.

indicator("SMC Long-Dip Dashboard v7", "SMC Long-Dip Dashboard v7", overlay = true, max_labels_count = 50)

